{
  "texts": [
    "On the other hand, there is a lack of systematic organization regarding the differences in types, domain orientations, realworld scenarios, etc., among various datasets.",
    "In order to reduce the learning curve, promote dataset research and technological innovation, broaden public awareness, we conduct a survey of LLM datasets.",
    "The objective is to provide researchers with a comprehensive and insightful perspective, facilitating a better understanding of the distribution and role of LLM datasets, thereby advancing the collective knowledge and application of LLMs.",
    "This paper summarizes existing representative datasets across five dimensions: pre-training corpora, instruction fine-tuning datasets, preference datasets, evaluation datasets, and traditional NLP datasets.",
    "Moreover, it presents new insights and ideas, discusses current bottlenecks, and explores future development trends."
  ]
}